    • Uses of ClientRequestInterceptor in org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.router.clientrm

      Classes in org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.router.clientrm that implement ClientRequestInterceptor 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractClientRequestInterceptor
      Implements the ClientRequestInterceptor interface and provides common functionality which can can be used and/or extended by other concrete intercepter classes.
      class  DefaultClientRequestInterceptor
      Extends the AbstractRequestInterceptorClient class and provides an implementation that simply forwards the client requests to the cluster resource manager.
      class  FederationClientInterceptor
      Extends the AbstractRequestInterceptorClient class and provides an implementation for federation of YARN RM and scaling an application across multiple YARN SubClusters.
